10 Year Congenital Warranty

The 10 year congenital warranty requires that you have had your puppy examined by a licensed veterinarian within the first 5 days of taking possession and have kept your puppy under regular veterinarian care and have your dog protected by Trupanion Pet Insurance for the first 10 years of the puppy/dogs life.

If the above conditions are met, Four Corner Puppies, LLC. warrants to the original purchaser the following: If within the first 3 year period your puppy is diagnosed with a life threatening congenital disorder, we will offer a replacement puppy of equivalent or lesser value at no cost to you. If within the remaining 7 years, your puppy is diagnosed with a life threatening congenital disorder, Four Corner Puppies, LLC. shall, upon presentation of reasonable, documented, actually incurred veterinary expenses associated with such diagnosed condition, at your option, either (i) issue a credit equal to fifty percent (50%) of the purchase price of your puppy(excluding any shipping cost), to be used toward the purchase of another puppy from Four Corner Puppies, LLC. (ii) reimburse you for your actually incurred veterinary expenses associated with such diagnosed condition, up to twenty-five percent of the original purchase price of your puppy.Shipping fees are not included in this warranty.
